#. <section class="sutta" id="sn56.13"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.13:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.13:0.2"
msgid "2. Dhammacakkappavattanavagga"
msgstr "2. Rolling Forth the Wheel of Dhamma"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.13:0.3"
msgid "13. Khandhasutta"
msgstr "13. Aggregates"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.13:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, ariyasaccāni."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four noble truths."

msgctxt "sn56.13:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri?"
msgstr "What four?"

#. VAR: dukkhasamudayaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhanirodhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ → dukkhasamudayo ariyasaccaṃ dukkhanirodho ariyasaccaṃ (bj, s1-3)
msgctxt "sn56.13:1.3"
msgid ""
"Dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhasamudayaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhanirodhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ."
msgstr ""
"The noble truths of suffering, the origin of suffering, the cessation of "
"suffering, and the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.13:2.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the noble truth of suffering?"

#. VAR: seyyathidaṃ → katame pañca? seyyathīdaṃ (bj) | katame pañca (s1-3, km) | seyyathīdaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "sn56.13:2.2"
msgid "‘Pañcupādānakkhandhā’ tissa vacanīyaṃ, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "You should say: ‘The five grasping aggregates’."

msgctxt "sn56.13:2.3"
msgid "rūpupādānakkhandho … pe … viññāṇupādānakkhandho."
msgstr "That is: form, feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness."

msgctxt "sn56.13:2.4"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ."
msgstr "This is called the noble truth of suffering."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.13:3.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, dukkhasamudayaṃ ariyasaccaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the noble truth of the origin of suffering?"

msgctxt "sn56.13:3.2"
msgid ""
"Yāyaṃ taṇhā ponobbhavikā nandirāgasahagatā tatratatrābhinandinī, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"It’s the craving that leads to future rebirth, mixed up with relishing and "
"greed, taking pleasure in various different realms. That is,"

msgctxt "sn56.13:3.3"
msgid "kāmataṇhā, bhavataṇhā, vibhavataṇhā."
msgstr ""
"craving for sensual pleasures, craving to continue existence, and craving to "
"end existence."

msgctxt "sn56.13:3.4"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhasamudayaṃ ariyasaccaṃ."
msgstr "This is called the noble truth of the origin of suffering."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.13:4.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, dukkhanirodhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the noble truth of the cessation of suffering?"

msgctxt "sn56.13:4.2"
msgid ""
"Yo tassāyeva taṇhāya asesavirāganirodho cāgo paṭinissaggo mutti anālayo—"
msgstr ""
"It’s the fading away and cessation of that very same craving with nothing "
"left over; giving it away, letting it go, releasing it, and not clinging to "
"it."

msgctxt "sn56.13:4.3"
msgid "idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhanirodhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ."
msgstr "This is called the noble truth of the cessation of suffering."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.426"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.13:5.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ?"
msgstr ""
"And what is the noble truth of the practice that leads to the cessation of "
"suffering?"

msgctxt "sn56.13:5.2"
msgid "Ayameva ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "It is simply this noble eightfold path, that is:"

msgctxt "sn56.13:5.3"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi—"
msgstr ""
"right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, "
"right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion."

msgctxt "sn56.13:5.4"
msgid "idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ."
msgstr ""
"This is called the noble truth of the practice that leads to the cessation "
"of suffering."

msgctxt "sn56.13:5.5"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri ariyasaccāni."
msgstr "These are the four noble truths."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.13:6.1"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.13:6.2"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
